creator: Robert Louis Stevenson
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 21 recordings of Autumn Fires, from Robert Louis Stevenson's classic A Child's Garden of Verses. This was the weekly poetry project for October 18-24, 2015. Read in English by ALMcClain; Algy Pug; Bruce Kachuk; Christie Crews; David Lawrence; Newgatenovelist; Garth Burton; Isaiah Barker; Joe Brenneman; Jael Baldwin; Jude; J. McDougall; Livia F.; Leonard Wilson; Matthew Carroll; Maria Kasper; mpvoice; DarkGoddess; SkyAlbatross; Sarah Marie and Rachel. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B Audiobook (7MB)
